			"updated_at": "2026-03-16T20:10:33Z",
			"body": "> This is for the GSOC project about the password strength indicator, which I’d like to contribute to. Please do help me out with what the next step is (after fixing the issues coderrabbitai found in this, which I will soon).\r\n\r\nIf you are looking to be selected for GSoC I'm not sure I understand why you have opened a PR with one of the project ideas rather than the bug fixes as the guidelines suggest. The PR doesn't meet the standards for a GSoC PR either - no AI disclosure and no video evidence to start with.\r\n\r\nThe PR is also meant to be final but you are asking for additional steps or guidance after the PR submission?",
