			"created_at": "2026-03-17T03:29:06Z",
			"updated_at": "2026-03-17T03:29:06Z",
			"body": "Make sure you read the GSoC guidelines that we publish and follow what is written there - both for issues to tackle and how to format your PR.\r\n\r\nWe are currently thinking that we need to remove this idea from the list entirely as it was created before current AI tools and we aren't sure that it is enough for the length of a GSoC project. That being said it might also be too much for a PR without having more defined requirements ahead of time (which is why we had this as a project and not an issue). Regardless the GSoC idea list was not a target for a potential contributor to select from, these are the actual projects people will complete over the course of GSoC, please make sure you read the PR guidelines again thoroughly.",
